{"tid":877121,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有時三部曲歌詞入面「你」係代表邊個？","createTime":"2018-10-26T06:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T09:05:56.000Z","uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5358f0ec6179909f9bbf625dd04e1ed8ed25267","tid":877121,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"有時：<br />\n這秒針　轉個彎<br />\n繁華極短暫<br />\n新愛或舊愛　沒盛載<br />\n最後也失散<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span>叫喚時間終止<br />\n永遠沒法預知哪日得<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span>重視<br />\n<br />\n重逢：<br />\n開打開的一剎<br />\n神聖的這一剎<br />\n無界別群眾 重聚相認明亮中<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span>已在半空 在我中 在虛空<br />\n<br />\n星塵：<br />\n尚有時空驅使中失散<br />\n穹蒼相擁後重逢自己<br />\n循環地愛出悲與喜<br />\n回憶空間中找到<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span><br />\n在每維度裡驗證　群星中千億生死"},{"pid":"33a77d1a3b877d7dac0cde160f108e4c10652dca","tid":877121,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c29ac774dfab4fe9fdf3990c35cd043b6f577d","tid":877121,"uid":196682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"&quot;你&quot;代表&quot;你&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此post完"},{"pid":"d9f70af858cffcb6fa13136efb392b370d8674c6","tid":877121,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0c29ac774dfab4fe9fdf3990c35cd043b6f577d","tid":877121,"uid":196682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"&quot;你&quot;代表&quot;你&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此post完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}